# AuthSpace — Login / Signup Page

A clean, secure, expert-designed login and signup page. Pure HTML + CSS + vanilla JS. No frameworks, no dependencies.

## Features
- 🎨 Dark-theme UI with DM Serif Display typography
- 🔒 Content-Security-Policy, X-Frame-Options, X-Content-Type-Options headers
- 🛡️ XSS protection via DOM-safe `createTextNode` sanitization
- 🤖 Bot detection via honeypot hidden field
- ⏱️ Rate limiting — 5 failed login attempts triggers a 30s lockout
- ✅ Client-side input validation (email regex, password length, name length)

## CI/CD
| Workflow | Trigger | Action |
|---|---|---|
| `ci.yml` | Every push to `main` | Validates HTML, deploys to GitHub Pages |
| `security.yml` | Every push/PR + weekly | TruffleHog secret scan, XSS pattern scan, CodeQL, header check |

## Live Demo
`https://Adhi2326.github.io/login-page`

## Setup
```bash
git clone https://github.com/Adhi2326/login-page.git
cd login-page
open index.html
```

## Alerts
GitHub will automatically email you at your account email when:
- Any workflow fails
- A security vulnerability is detected (CodeQL / TruffleHog)
- A PR is raised that breaks security checks

To configure: **GitHub → Settings → Notifications → Actions**